data.text: In the historical sciences and other humanities disciplines, digital tools have become an integral part of everyday academic life. This collection brings together the best publicly accessible tools, source collections and platforms for digital history and related disciplines.
The Proceedings of the Old Bailey
Framework for Information Literacy for Higher Education
Stuff You Missed in History Class
